        "content": "### ðŸ“Œ Node: Google Sheets1\n\n- **Type:** Google Sheets (Read)\n- **Function:** Reads all data from the specified sheet.\n- **Why it's used:** Fetches rows to process for lead magnet generation.\n- **Sheet Name:** Sheet1 (gid=0)\n- **Authentication:** Google Service Account\n"
