        "content": "### ðŸ“Œ Node: Loop Over Items\n\n- **Type:** Split In Batches (n8n-nodes-base.splitInBatches)\n- **Function:** Processes each row one at a time.\n- **Why it's used:** Ensures efficient row-by-row processing to control API load.\n- **Options:**\n  - `reset: false`\n"
