        "content": "### ðŸ“Œ Node: If\n\n- **Type:** Conditional Check\n- **Function:** Filters rows where:\n  - `Topic` is **not empty**\n  - `Content` is **empty**\n- **Why it's used:** To skip rows that already have generated content or are missing topics.\n- **Condition Logic:**\n  - `Topic` â†’ `notEmpty`\n  - `Content` â†’ `empty`\n- **Combinator:** `AND`\n"
